NPCName "Eduardo"
Location "Sandover"
Description ""
Unknown_Desc "You see an old man with a dog."
Known_Desc "It's Eduardo, the retired scavenger."
Detailed_Desc "This is Eduardo, the retired scavenger. Next to him is his trusty dog Starkey."

/* Regular nodes */

Node "START"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Use teh logic sk1llz to f1nd 0ut where si teh start!"
      options {
          int=1 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Default starting node. (All cases not covered below will start with this node)" linkto "A"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If PC has meat jerky in inventory, and this is the first time the PC talks to Eduardo, and PC is not stupid." linkto "B"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If PC is not stupid, has talked to Eduardo before and PC is not currently followed by Starkey." linkto "C"  notes ""
          int=1 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If PC is stupid, has talked to Eduardo before and is not followed by Starkey." linkto "IS"  notes ""
          int=1 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If PC has threatened to kill Starkey (reached node B_A_A) (note: this can't happen for stupid PC)." linkto "D"  notes ""
          int=1 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If PC has borrowed Starkey and finished the quest to find the missing scavenger, and Starkey is not dead." linkto "E"  notes ""
          int=1 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If PC has borrowed Starkey and finished the quest to find the missing scavenger, and Starkey is dead." linkto "G"  notes ""
          int=1 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If PC has borrowed Starkey and not finished the quest to find the missing scavenger, and Starkey is not dead." linkto "H"  notes ""
          int=1 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If PC has borrowed Starkey and not finished the quest to find the missing scavenger, and Starkey is dead." linkto "F"  notes ""
          int=1 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "If Starkey is dead, and PC has talked to Eduardo about that before." linkto "F_A_A_A_A_B"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Hi, I don't believe we've met. I'm Eduardo, and this is my trusty servant Starkey."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What do you do here, Eduardo?" linkto "A"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Servant? Looks more like a dog to me." linkto "A_B"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Nice to meet you, Eduardo." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Woof, woof [point at the dog]!" linkto "A_SA"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Ewwa doo?" linkto "A_SB"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A_A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Oh, not much. I used to be a scavenger, but I'm retired now. I mostly just help the younger scavengers with advice."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can I ask you something else?" linkto "A_A_A"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I doubt anyone could learn anything from you. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see. Nice talking to you, goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A_A_A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Sure, what would you like to know?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me more about your dog." linkto "A_B_A"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm looking for a scavenger that's gone missing. Would you mind if I borrowed Starkey to help me find her?" linkto "A_B_B"  notes "Only if PC have taken the quest to find the lost scavenger"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You don't happen to be associated with The Hounds?" linkto "A_A_A_B"  notes "Only if PC has been to the Hounds"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Uh, nothing. Bye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A_A_A_B"
notes ""
{
NPCText "The who?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Another question please." linkto "A_A_A"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Nevermind." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A_B"
notes ""
{
NPCText "He used to be a tracker dog, but we've both grown too old to work. At least I have - Starkey's senses are still keen. They always were..."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tracking dog, eh? Tell me more." linkto "A_B_A"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm looking for a scavenger that's gone missing. Would you mind if I borrowed Starkey to help me find her?" linkto "A_B_B"  notes "Only if PC have taken the quest to find the lost scavenger"
              }
}
Node "A_B_A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Well, there's not much to tell. He used to assist me while scavenging. Once he got me into a lot of trouble just to find an ancient can of dried brahmin meat, but more often he showed me to some really nice scavenges. Now he's just a good friend, since I'm too old to work. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm looking for a scavenger that's gone missing. Would you mind if I borrowed Starkey to help me find her?" linkto "A_B_B"  notes "Only if PC have taken the quest to find the lost scavenger"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I understand. See you around." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A_B_B"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Oh yes, Eleanor, right? Yes, of course. I'm sure Starkey will find her."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thanks. Come on Starkey, let's go." linkto "done"  notes "Starkey the dog will now follow the PC."
              }
}
Node "A_SA"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Yes, Starkey is a dog. A tracker dog. You can pat him if you like."
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Me take buhr-ow... dog? For... Uhhh... Find Elli-nor ladie!" linkto "A_SA_A"  notes "Only if PC has the quest to find Eleanor."
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Giggle.]" linkto "A_SA_B"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A_SA_A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "You want to borrow Starkey?"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Uh-huh!" linkto "A_SA_A_A"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Nuh-uh!" linkto "A_SA_A_B"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A_SA_A_A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Oh, I see, you're trying to find Eleanor, right? Yes, of course you can have Starkey. He is a very good tracking dog, I'm sure you two will find her."
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "????" linkto "A_SA_A_A_A"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A_SA_A_A_A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "[He gesticulate with his arms, trying to explain.] You find E-le-a-nor. Star-key help you."
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Uh, okay." linkto "done"  notes "Starkey will now follow the PC until he finds Eleanor."
              }
}
Node "A_SA_A_B"
notes ""
{
NPCText "All right then. Is there anything I can help you with, friend? You want help?"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Uhh... Bye, bye!" linkto "A_SA_A_B_A"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A_SA_A_B_A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Take care, my friend, take care."
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Done.]" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A_SA_B"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Is there anything I can do for you, friend? You want help?"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Me take buhr-ow... dog? For... Uhhh... Find Elli-nor lady!" linkto "A_SA_A"  notes "Only if PC has the quest to find Eleanor."
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Uhh... Bye, bye!" linkto "A_SA_A_B_A"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A_SB"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Very good, Eduardo, that's my name. What is your name? [He points at you.]"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Staaa kiiii (heh heh)" linkto "A_SB_A"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Ohhh..." linkto "A_SB_A_A"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "A_SB_A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "No, no, Starkey is the dog. [He points at the dog.] Starkey dog."
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No? Do...?" linkto "A_SB_A_A"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Me take buhr-ow... dog? For... Uhhh... Find Elli-nor lady!" linkto "A_SA_A"  notes "Only if PC has the quest to find Eleanor."
              }
}
Node "A_SB_A_A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Ahh, why do even bother?"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Done.]" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "B"
notes "If PC has meat jerky in his inventory"
{
NPCText "[The dog runs up to you and waves its tail hysterically. It barks.] Sit Starkey. Sit! [The dog stops barking and sit down.]"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Whoah, keep that thing away from me!" linkto "B_A"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's a well trained dog you've got there." linkto "B_B"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "B_A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "I'm terribly sorry, sir. I've never seen him behave like this before."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yes, I'm sure. I've never killed a dog either, but I might have to make an exception now." linkto "B_A_A"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's alright. " linkto "B_A_B"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "B_A_A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "W-what? You don't have to kill Starkey! He's everything I've got! He's my only friend!"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well, my life is the only one I've got, and I'm not going to let that crazy dog of yours take it away from me!" linkto "B_A_A_A"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "See? Not so fun being scared like that. The next time I see you that dog better be in a collar, or you might as well dig his grave already. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes "If PC talks to Eduardo again, he will start at node 4."
              }
}
Node "B_A_A_A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Please, don't hurt Starkey! He's a tracker dog, see? I think he smelled something..."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What? Are you saying that I smell bad? Step aside, old man! That dog is going down!" linkto "combat"  notes "Eduardo runs away, and combat is ended if the PC does nothing. If PC tries to talk to him again, he will run away."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "... and?" linkto "B_A_A_A_A"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "B_A_A_A_A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "[He sounds very nervous.] I - I think he smelled some meat jerky! He's mad about meat jerky, can't control himself."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "First your dog attacks me, then you say I smell like meat jerky. You better think fast, before I lose my temper." linkto "B_A_A_A_A_A"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That meat jerky is mine, and you can't have it. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "B_A_A_A_A_A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "What? I didn't mean to... Look, I'm sorry, okay? Please, don't hurt me!"
      options {
          int=4 linkflags custom_proc Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Too late, asshole! Step aside, that dog is going down." linkto "combat"  notes ""
          int=4 linkflags custom_proc Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "All right, I'll let you go. For now. But the next time I see you that dog better be in a collar, or you might as well dig his grave already. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "B_A_B"
notes ""
{
NPCText "[He looks relieved.] Say hello to this fine man Starkey. [The dog put forth its right paw in a \"shake hands\" motion.] I'm Eduardo. You're already introduced to Starkey. "
 NPCFemaleText "[He looks relieved.] Say hello to this fine woman Starkey. [The dog put forth its right paw in a \"shake hands\" motion.] I'm Eduardo. You're already introduced to Starkey. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So what are you doing here in Sandover, Eduardo?" linkto "A_B"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How cute. I've a train to catch, so I'll see you later Eduardo." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "B_B"
notes ""
/* Skill checks for node B_B */

      define_skill_check Skill_Check_000_Speech {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = 0;
      onsuccess => A2_2_1a;
      onfailure => A2_2_1b;
      }
      define_skill_check Skill_Check_001_Speech {
      skill_num = 15;
      difficulty_modifier = 0;
      onsuccess => B_B_Aa;
      onfailure => B_B_Ab;
      }

{
NPCText "Why, thank you. I think he smelled something. You don't happen to have some meat jerky in your pockets?"
      options {
          int=4 linkflags skill_check Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Lie] Uhh, nope. Sorry." linkto "Skill_Check_001_Speech"  notes "Skill check difficulty modifier need tweaking"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, I do." linkto "B_B_B"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Of course. Here you go Starkey [give some meat jerky to the dog.]" linkto "B_B_B"  notes "Remove a piece of meat jerky from PCs inventory."
              }
}
Node "B_B_Aa"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Damn, I guess I'm getting a bit rusty. Starkey used to be able to smell meat jerky from miles away."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Really?" linkto "B_B_Aa_A"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, I do have some meat jerky. You can have it for 10 bucks." linkto "B_B_Aa_B"  notes "Removes one meat jerky from PC inventory, and adds 10 caps."
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Maybe he's not such a good dog after all?" linkto "B_B_Aa_C"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "B_B_Aa_A"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Yeah. He's a tracker dog, you know. Used to assist me while scavenging. Once he got me into a lot of trouble just to find an ancient can of dried brahmin meat, but more often he showed me to some really nice scavenges. Now he's just a good friend, since I'm too old to work."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I see. Let me ask you something else." linkto "B_B_Aa_B_A_A"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I understand. See you around." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
