notes ""
{
NPCText "Sure, what would you like to know?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm looking for a scavenger that's gone missing. Would you mind if I borrowed Starkey to help me find her?" linkto "A_B_B"  notes "Only if PC have taken the quest to find the lost scavenger"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You don't happen to be associated with The Hounds?" linkto "A_A_A_B"  notes "Only if PC has been to The Hounds"
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Uh, nothing. Bye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "B_B_Aa_B"
notes ""
{
NPCText "Ten bucks, eh? What do you say Starkey, do we want some jerky today? Do we want some sweet brahmin jerky? [The dog waves its tail in ecstacy.] Here's ten. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[Continue.]" linkto "B_B_Aa_B_A"  notes ""
              }
}
