notes ""
{
NPCText "No. Listen, I'm actually quite busy, so if there's nothing urgent you wanted to say, I'd rather you left me alone."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What the hell is that supposed to mean? I don't have any meat jerky, I told you!" linkto "B_B_Aa_C"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, I had some questions..." linkto "B_B_Aa_C_A"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Oh well. See you around Eduardo." linkto "done"  notes ""
