notes ""
{
NPCText "[Starkey is growling deeply.] Calm down Starkey. [He looks up at you.] I don't think I can trust you enough."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well fuck you too, asshole! If I can't have that dog, I'm gonna make damn sure you can't have him either!" linkto "D_A_A_A"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "All right then." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
